{"tid":326379,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"政府避談會否合併補選","createTime":"2017-07-18T03:09:46.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-18T08:00:44.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"cfe893da2b301a9f3e04cf5f52b44ccfef0a83fc","tid":326379,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T03:09:46.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=20093268&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170718\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D20093268%26category_guid%3D4104%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170718&d=nQDymLHpC61b3hBQzZxSKR4KspRE1ZdqvS7v6cf6aI4%3D&h=3858d11d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D20093268%26category_guid%3D4104%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170718&h=9ca8ae90\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=20093268&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170718</a><br />\n<br />\n政府避談會否合併補選<br />\n<br />\n要聞&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼<br />\n<br />\n￼<br />\n<br />\n政制及內地事務局長聶德權<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】當局會否將兩次DQ案引發的補選合併進行，影響未來議會勢力分佈，尤其民主派會否在地區直選失守，失去分組點票否決權極為關鍵，政制及內地事務局長聶德權昨被問到會否分開兩場補選時未有正面回應，只稱會按照程序和相關法例，以及場地因素等安排。<br />\n<br />\n稱由選管會決定<br />\n<br />\n若當局將青政梁頌恆及游蕙禎議席出缺，連同最近4議員的議席即合共6席一併補選，則九龍西及新界東有兩個議席同時補選，勢由民主派與建制派瓜分，民主派在地區直選議席極有可能不過半，在分組點票中失去否決權。<br />\n聶德權昨稱，有關梁游案的司法程序仍在進行，終審法院下月會審議其申請上訴許可，要視乎聆訊結果才知整個司法程序是否完成，才能決定何時進行補選。至於另外4位被DQ議員，聶指尊重高等法院有關裁決，按照程序，立法會秘書長會在21日內刊憲宣佈議席出缺，選舉管理委員會將按法例及實際情況考慮如何處理補選。<br />\n但聶指目前未知4人會否上訴，故具體工作仍未確定，他強調4議員的案件於上屆政府經諮詢法律意見而作出，非單單律政司意見，政府也有諮詢外面法律意見。<br />\n■記者姚國雄<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞<br />\n<br />\n￼<br />\n<br />\n長毛「重返」議會　秘書處阻受訪<br />\n<br />\n要聞&nbsp;5小時前<br />\n<br />\n￼<br />\n<br />\n泛民今開會商財會對策<br />\n<br />\n要聞&nbsp;5小時前<br />\n<br />\n￼<br />\n<br />\n議員生涯僅9個月　姚松炎：揭中共邪惡<br />\n<br />\n要聞&nbsp;5小時前"},{"pid":"c2f942802de44a08b22944bd75dbb2a2ad12a903","tid":326379,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T03:23:22.000Z","msg":"肯定會，單票制共狗肯定輸，比例代表制先可以搶到議席；唔通搞咁多野DQ完果班友又俾佢地入返去咩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e38c607c9872ab51db5e67087775aeaeb25631ac","tid":326379,"uid":20227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T03:30:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5d7b7dd037327321f8ef20b2527fa6f8bfe024f7","tid":326379,"uid":22858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T03:33:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63567f4d6f1f64e27b54bd9907e1d4249c67d034","tid":326379,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T03:58:50.000Z","msg":"等梁游終審判決後就可以決定是否補選"},{"pid":"c0e6d0aa31aca043db358eb8f367c960949b6e1b","tid":326379,"uid":100048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T04:00:57.000Z","msg":"分開補浪費人力物力"},{"pid":"86dc63841c1d55c2d7e913bfbc3e2da3e2e9dcc6","tid":326379,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T04:02:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>分開補浪費人力物力</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n不如中央欽點好唔好 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ed6b0eec6836077f1cfda8ddf973998fb752fb0","tid":326379,"uid":100048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T04:04:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>分開補浪費人力物力</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n不如中央欽點好唔好 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔好"},{"pid":"73d0805f3ff027dce878f9826c20da30ebb7c45c","tid":326379,"uid":20227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T04:10:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"432dd1dd482941f4